* No root import; leaf-level file.
* No edits to committed bridge files or Secondary's
  per-branch-chain file.
* No Lane B / Cor 8.32 / Jacobson / T001 / faithful-flatness /
  final-acyclicity / T005 / T013 / T016 content. -/

